                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GEORGE TOMLIN</hi> (19)</persName> was indicted<rs id="t18640919-863-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18640919-863-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18640919-863-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp> for a like offence.</rs>
